  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CITICC Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC is considering an investment in partnership with CITIC Construction Co., Limited (CITICC) to establish a greenfield holding company (the Platform) to facilitate the development of affordable housing projects in Sub-Saharan Africa (the Project).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project will have the following development impacts: (i) Increase affordable housing supply thereby contributing to the alleviation of the current housing deficit in Sub-Saharan Africa; (ii) Create thousands of both direct and indirect jobs during construction and the operating phase of the housing communities; (iii) Transform the affordable housing sector by demonstrating the viability and affordability of this sector whilst maintaining IFC&apos;&apos;s environmental and social standards; (iv) Enhance local supply linkages through sourcing from local suppliers and creating critical mass of market demand to justify local manufacturing capacity build-up; and  (v) Contribute to more sustainable urbanization through providing much needed urban infrastructure in good quality and at fair cost.</narrative>
  </description>
